Project: **JagranEcoFest** 🌍🌿 — World Environment Day 2026
Crafted with passion by Starverse.

A mobile-first, multi-step event registration web app built for the NSS Unit
of Jagran College of Arts, Science and Commerce. Students can register for
Poster & Slogan Making and Quiz competitions through an intuitive, nature-themed
interface — all powered by a Google Sheets backend.

This project is open-source and created for educational, creative, and
community-driven purposes under the NSS motto: *"Not Me But You"*.

"Starverse" branding, visual identity, and custom assets may not be reused
commercially without permission.

Made with ❤️ by Starverse — for the environment, for the community.
